            <ab>OIM 19297, recto: (1) [...]...daughter of Psenamounis, 1/12 silver [kite] 1/2 obol for the price (2) [of oil] of Pharmouthi, has written Esminis (3) on Egyptian year 38, Pachons 5; Taminis her sister(?), (4) 1/2 obol, written.</ab>
